      "para_id": "Q004157.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) Amar-Suena , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters : Ur-sagaĝu , the royal scribe , child of Lugal-kagina , is your servant ."
    }
  ],
